---
import CourseLayout from '../layouts/CourseLayout.astro';
---

<CourseLayout title="Module 3: Complaint Resolution" currentModule={3}>
  
  <span class="text-sky-600 font-bold tracking-wider uppercase text-sm">Topic 3 of 6</span>
  <h1 class="text-4xl font-extrabold text-slate-900 mt-2 mb-8">Participant Complaint Resolution</h1>

  <div class="prose prose-lg prose-slate max-w-none">
    
    <p class="lead text-xl text-slate-600 mb-8">
      A complaint is an opportunity to improve. Participants have a fundamental right to voice dissatisfaction without fear of losing their services or being treated poorly.
    </p>

    <div class="bg-indigo-50 border-l-4 border-indigo-600 p-6 rounded-r-lg mb-10">
      <h3 class="text-indigo-900 font-bold text-xl m-0 mb-2">The "No Retaliation" Guarantee</h3>
      <p class="text-indigo-800 m-0">
        It is illegal for an agency or a worker to retaliate against a participant for filing a complaint. You cannot:
      </p>
      <ul class="list-disc ml-5 mt-2 text-indigo-800">
        <li>Arrive late on purpose.</li>
        <li>Be rude or silent during your shift.</li>
        <li>Threaten to quit.</li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-6">Your Role in the Process</h3>
    <div class="space-y-6">
      
      <div class="flex gap-6 items-start p-4 bg-white rounded-lg shadow-sm border border-slate-100">
        <div class="bg-slate-100 p-3 rounded-full text-slate-500">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-6 w-6" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 11a7 7 0 01-7 7m0 0a7 7 0 01-7-7m7 7v4m0 0H8m4 0h4m-4-8a3 3 0 01-3-3V5a3 3 0 116 0v6a3 3 0 01-3 3z" />
          </svg>
        </div>
        <div>
          <strong class="text-lg text-slate-900 block">Listen Respectfully</strong>
          <p class="text-sm text-slate-600">If a participant complains to you, do not get defensive. Say: <em>"I understand you are frustrated. I want to make sure this is addressed. Let me have my supervisor call you, or I can give you the number."</em></p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="flex gap-6 items-start p-4 bg-white rounded-lg shadow-sm border border-slate-100">
        <div class="bg-slate-100 p-3 rounded-full text-slate-500">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-6 w-6" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M15.232 5.232l3.536 3.536m-2.036-5.036a2.5 2.5 0 113.536 3.536L6.5 21.036H3v-3.572L16.732 3.732z" />
          </svg>
        </div>
        <div>
          <strong class="text-lg text-slate-900 block">Report Upward</strong>
          <p class="text-sm text-slate-600">You must report the complaint to your supervisor immediately. Even if you think it is minor, it must be logged in the agency's complaint registry.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>

    <div class="flex justify-between items-center pt-8 mt-12 border-t border-slate-200">
        <a href="/module-2" class="text-slate-500 hover:text-sky-600 font-semibold flex items-center gap-2">
            ← Previous: Incident Reporting
        </a>
        <a href="/module-4" class="bg-sky-600 hover:bg-sky-700 text-white font-bold py-3 px-8 rounded-lg shadow-lg flex items-center gap-2">
            Next: Policies & Procedures →
        </a>
    </div>

  </div>
</CourseLayout>